points to close at 15766. The
Nasdaq fell five and the S&amp;P

01:31.558 --> 01:37.030 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
500 dropped 22. All this was
driven by another sharp drop in
oil prices to just over $26.50

01:37.030 --> 01:40.067 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
a barrel.

01:40.067 --> 01:47.140 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
