16 is a pretty good batting
average.

02:22.843 --> 02:27.781 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: NOAA had already
announced that 2015 was the
second warmest year in the
United

02:27.781 --> 02:33.286 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
States since record-keeping
started 121 years ago.

02:33.286 --> 02:39.693 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: In Pakistan,
Islamist militants killed at
least 18 students and two
teachers

02:39.693 --> 02:45.132 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
at a university today and
wounded 23 others. The attackers
stormed the school in the
northwestern

02:45.132 --> 02:51.772 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
city of Charsadda, before being
cornered and killed by soldiers.

02:51.772 --> 02:59.112 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Ambulance sirens wailed outside
Bacha Khan University even as
the battle raged inside.

02:59.112 --> 03:04.418 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Four militants had sneaked in
under cover of early morning fog
and started shooting.

03:04.418 --> 03:08.255 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MAN (through translator): We
heard firing from the back of
the campus. We thought maybe

03:08.255 --> 03:11.124 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
some people were fighting. Then
the firing increased. Then he
said, get into the rooms.

03:11.124 --> 03:13.193 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Don't go out.

03:13.193 --> 03:16.830 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MAN (through translator): There
was so much panic and fear that
a friend of mine jumped

03:16.830 --> 03:20.534 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
from the university building.
The building is very high, yet
he jumped from it in because

03:20.534 --> 03:25.205 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
he was so scared. We saw the
militants chanting, "Allah is
greatest."

03:25.205 --> 03:30.310 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Police and
military forces descended on the
campus and counterattacked.

03:30.310 --> 03:34.681 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Washington Post reporter Tim
Craig tracked the operation from
Islamabad.

03:34.681 --> 03:38.819 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
TIM CRAIG, Washington Post: It
was quite foggy, so they
actually used helicopters to
sort

03:38.819 --> 03:44.324 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
of see the ground of the campus,
because it was really foggy. So,
helicopters were used.

03:44.324 --> 03:48.562 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
They rappelled commandos onto
the school grounds to sort of
fight the terrorists.

03:48.562 --> 03:53.100 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Friends and
family waited for news of loved
ones as a prolonged gun battle

03:53.100 --> 03:57.537 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
followed. Police say they had
to proceed with caution.

03:57.537 --> 04:00.941 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SAEED KHAN WAZIR, Police Chief
(through translator): This was a
short lived operation,
approximately

04:00.941 --> 04:05.912 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
two hours in duration, in which
time we finished the militants.
Two of them were on the hostel

04:05.912 --> 04:08.982 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
roof top, but there was some
confusion that they might be
students, as they were
young-looking.

04:08.982 --> 04:12.619 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Otherwise, we could easily have
targeted them in the beginning.

04:12.619 --> 04:17.924 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: A breakaway
faction of the Pakistani Taliban
claimed responsibility,

04:17.924 --> 04:26.032 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
but the main Taliban group
called it un-Islamic. The attack
echoed the 2014 massacre at a
grade

04:26.032 --> 04:33.373 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
