monastery. Satellite photos
obtained by the Associated Press
show

06:08.068 --> 06:13.406 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
St. Elijah's Monastery in Mosul
was leveled in September of
2014. It had stood for 1,400

06:13.406 --> 06:15.575 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
years.

06:15.575 --> 06:20.447 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
REV. PAUL THABIT HABIB, Iraqi
Priest (through translator): It
became a spiritual place for

06:20.447 --> 06:24.618 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the Christians to visit and to
have religious ceremonies there.
The monastery attracted

06:24.618 --> 06:29.556 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
