became a very important place
for the history of the church

06:31.858 --> 06:34.160 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
in Iraq.

06:34.160 --> 06:38.832 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: In the past 18
months, the Islamic State has
damaged or destroyed hundreds

06:38.832 --> 06:43.036 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
of ancient cultural sites
in Syria and Iraq.

06:43.036 --> 06:48.008 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
GWEN IFILL: Back in this
country, Senate Democrats
blocked a Republican bill to
toughen screenings

06:48.008 --> 06:54.014 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
