06:59.419 --> 07:02.689 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
SEN. RICHARD DURBIN (D),
Illinois: I don't understand why
the Republicans in the Senate

07:02.689 --> 07:07.694 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
