08:07.454 --> 08:14.227 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: And an automobile
with special status is going on
the auction block in
Philadelphia.

08:14.227 --> 08:20.133 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Pope Francis used the black Fiat
during his visit to the U.S.
last September. The auction

08:20.133 --> 08:25.405 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
is set for January 29. Proceeds
will go to the Roman Catholic
archdiocese and the Children's

08:25.405 --> 08:28.875 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Hospital of Philadelphia.

08:28.875 --> 08:36.282 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And coming up on
the "NewsHour": the latest on
Flint, Michigan's toxic water

08:36.282 --> 08:42.522 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
