spreading virus that causes
child deformities; a call to
de-emphasize

08:42.522 --> 08:53.066 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
test scores in college
applications; and much more.

08:53.066 --> 09:04.911 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Truth be told, the
water crisis in Flint, Michigan,
was a story that has been

09:04.911 --> 09:10.049 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
unfolding for years, and has
only recently begun attracting
regional attention. But now

09:10.049 --> 09:14.020 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the massive lead contamination
of the city's drinking water is
very much on the national

09:14.020 --> 09:16.956 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
radar.

09:16.956 --> 09:20.827 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
