double and in some cases triple
the levels of lead in their
blood,

09:20.827 --> 09:23.830 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
and a federal emergency was
declared last weekend.

09:23.830 --> 09:28.034 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Today, in Detroit, President
Obama addressed the troubles in
Flint.

09:28.034 --> 09:31.938 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA, President of the
United States: I know that if I
was a parent up there, I

09:31.938 --> 09:45.752 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
would be beside myself that my
kids' health could be at risk.
It is a reminder of why

09:45.752 --> 09:53.526 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
you can't shortchange basic
services that we provide to our
people and that we together

09:53.526 --> 09:57.330 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
provide as a government to make
sure that public health and
safety is preserved.

09:57.330 --> 09:59.466 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(APPLAUSE)

09:59.466 --> 10:05.271 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: In fact, Michigan
Governor Rick Snyder has
apologized, and pledged to take

10:05.271 --> 10:09.309 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
new steps to protect the
community. Snyder himself is
under increasing pressure to
detail

10:09.309 --> 10:13.046 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
what his administration
knew, and when.

10:13.046 --> 10:17.450 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And in Flint, there's plenty of
anger and questions over who is
to blame.

10:17.450 --> 10:21.054 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
The "NewsHour"'s William
Brangham is just back from Flint
with this report.

10:21.054 --> 10:22.989 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: This
is how bad it's gotten.

10:22.989 --> 10:25.492 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
WOMAN: A case of water.

10:25.492 --> 10:29.229 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
WOMAN: A case of water for this
house. Did she get a filter?

10:29.229 --> 10:31.464 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: In Flint,
Michigan, the sheriff's
department is going
door-to-door,

10:31.464 --> 10:35.435 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
