address, Michigan Governor Rick
Snyder heard to apologize.

10:44.844 --> 10:49.048 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
GOV. RICK SNYDER (R), Michigan:
To you, the people of Flint, I
say tonight, as I have

10:49.048 --> 10:52.986 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
