and I will fix it.

10:52.986 --> 10:57.790 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Why? Because,
for a year-and-a-half, despite
repeated claims from officials
that

10:57.790 --> 11:02.295 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
