damage to the human body.

11:05.698 --> 11:08.668 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
KIM STREBY, Mother: It's every
kid on the block, it's every
baby on the block, it's

11:08.668 --> 11:11.738 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
everybody, every old person.

11:11.738 --> 11:15.441 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: One of Kim
Streby's two sons, like
potentially thousands of other

11:15.441 --> 11:19.212 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
kids in Flint, has elevated
levels of lead in his blood.

11:19.212 --> 11:27.921 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
KIM STREBY: I was absolutely
disgusted to think that we are
paying an enormous price

11:27.921 --> 11:34.093 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
for water that is dangerous,
that we can't use.

11:34.093 --> 11:38.064 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: The crisis
began five years ago, because
the city of Flint was trying

11:38.064 --> 11:43.937 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
